'''Kernuack Nowedga''', po '''Curnoack Nowedga''', ew idden version screefez wor an [[tavaz Kernuack]]. Ma an letherednanz ma a profya gweel defneth a dhewetha manner an tavaz bew, hebm ew en [[17ves kansblydhen|17ves]] ha [[18ves kansblydhen|18ves cansblethenio]]. [[Richard Gendall]] ew kenja ledyer a'n scoal letherednans ma. [[Teer ha Tavaz]] ew an bagaz chief a promovya Curnoack Nowedga. Ma [[Cussel an Tavas Kernuack]] a rewlya savon an radden-tavaz. 

Ma an try letherednanz orol usya gerrio ha whathe leverianjo a Gernuack Dewethaz (en arbednick '[[Kernowek Unys Amendys|UCR]]-West'), bez pidnfenten a letherednanz Kernuack Nowedga ew screffanjo an [[teylu Boson]] ha'ga huthmans ([[Thomas Tonkin|Tonkin]], [[William Gwavas|Gwavas]], h.e.).

